{"tid":926832,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇咗《比悲傷更悲傷的故事》既入嚟討論吓⋯","createTime":"2018-12-03T17:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T16:46:09.000Z","uid":222196,"like":64,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"95a544233e4b0fe7da9c99b0575dd64b95ad25dc","tid":926832,"uid":222196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"真係好耐無被感動過<br />\n所以忍唔住要開post講一講<br />\n究竟一個男人要幾愛一個人<br />\n先會偉大到去幫自己最愛既女人去搵第二個男人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我睇到呢度D眼淚忍唔住係咁流<br />\n可能我有近似經歷呱<br />\n<br />\n不過全場聽到好多飲泣聲<br />\n坐我旁邊條肥仔拖住條囡入場<br />\n仆佢個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊得仲大聲過條囡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你係男女主角你會點做⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者睇完有咩感覺？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d746600c0d2498aecc48660549a31daf262237","tid":926832,"uid":222196,"like":5,"dislike":25,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講下自己經歷先<br />\n<br />\n曾經前女友同我講<br />\n公司有個男仔追緊<br />\n當時我哋關係仲係拖拖拉拉<br />\n<br />\n當時我同佢講<br />\n你都要為自己將來幸福打算下㗎<br />\n如果你覺得佢俾到你<br />\n你咪嘗試接受下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完後悔到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋依家真係變咗一個好幸福既家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87092a8914cb43b92ea5648345221786a8c01e3","tid":926832,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d658e7fe6d9505637bee3800a907b946e725c8bf","tid":926832,"uid":53944,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"爸打係米睇岩岩朗豪坊 10:45？ <br />\n同場聽到勁多人喊⋯"},{"pid":"60dda3cd9afa3bafc3fd07677f4190013fbab6ff","tid":926832,"uid":222196,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d658e7fe6d9